and current financial statements of all Registrants; therefore, the effect of the change was recorded through earnings as a prior
period adjustment for the amounts related to the unregulated businesses of Southern Company and Southern Power. Amounts
related to the traditional electric operating companies and the natural gas distribution utilities were reflected as adjustments to
regulatory assets, consistent with the expected regulatory treatment.
