REPORT OF INDEPENDENT REGISTERED PUBLIC ACCOUNTING FIRM
To the stockholders and the Board of Directors of Alabama Power Company
Opinion on the Financial Statement Schedule
We have audited the financial statements of Alabama Power Company (Alabama Power) (a wholly-owned subsidiary of The
Southern Company) as of December 31, 2020 and 2019, and for each of the three years in the period ended December 31, 2020,
and have issued our report thereon dated February 17, 2021; such report is included elsewhere in this Form 10-K. Our audits also
